Usage:
    rails generate action_cable:install

Description:
    Creates the Ruby, CoffeeScript, and Redis configuration files
    to support Action Cable.

Example:
    rails generate action_cable:install

    Necessary files to support Action Cable.
        Application Cable: app/channels/application_cable/channel.rb
                           app/channels/application_cable/connection.rb
        CoffeeScript:      app/assets/javascripts/channels/interesting_name_channel.coffee
        Redis config:      config/redis/cable.yml
